body_html: @LeavesBreathe, I took a brief of the paper you plan to replicate in TF. I suspect you'll encounter some nuances. E.g., some operations may not have support for complex64 as time being. They are minor problems because they can be easily patched by updating a few .cc file to expand the types they support.

body: @LeavesBreathe, I took a brief of the paper you plan to replicate in TF. I suspect you'll encounter some nuances. E.g., some operations may not have support for complex64 as time being. They are minor problems because they can be easily patched by updating a few .cc file to expand the types they support.
